    "In addition, we also report the number of useful invariants in gray brackets.",
    "Useful here means that the verifier cannot complete the verification task without the invariant.",
    "ChatGPT can generate valid loop invariants.",
    "We find that ChatGPT can generate valid loop invariants for 75 out of 106 tasks (as validated by Frama-C).",
    "Note that ChatGPT proposes loop invariant candidates for all 106 tasks and by manual inspection we found that some of the generated loop invariant candidates are still meaningful, even though they are not validated by Frama-C. An example is shown in Figure 2."
